<br>
The thing people forget tho, is that PvP should class roles within a group. Everyone needs a role. <br>
<br>
My opinons thus far<br>
<br>
- Rangers. Fricken own. I can't tell you how happy i am with bow changes. Im sure they will be nerfed tho.<br>
- Mages. I dont see much of a change. Pets are annoying but nothing like Epic was pre-60. Does anyone fear the mage? (sorry Mearis)<br>
- Rogues. Every group needs one. Look at Solidus' kills! They need some kind of DS damage mitigation tho. Qument killed one 1 on 1 just with his reverse DS.<br>
- Wizard. No change that ive seen.<br>
- Cleric. No change that ive seen.<br>
- Druid. Poor druids. I don't even bother dispelling their dots. I laugh in the face of their nukes. Not sure what their role is other than porter/healer.<br>
- Zerker. Jesus, nerf the snare. Such a nice pvp class. They're the new Sks, imo. <br>
- Warrior. In a group, owns. Mele changes really helped the suck jousters (such as myself)<br>
- Shammy. Everything lands on me now. Shammys must be happy. Can they even be killed?<br>
- SK. Boring. Does anyone fear them on test? Ill take a war or zerker over them any day<br>
- Pally. Up their DPS or something. Pallys have been shafted.<br>
- Monk. Awesome class, but involves so much running around. Don;t you guys ever get tired of running, clicking on epic, jousting, running, yawn.<br>
- Necros. They're just as godly as always, which is why I target them first. In group pvp they arent nearly as deadly as solo.<br>
- bard. No change. They run real fast and can dispell real good.  A passive aggressive class if there ever was one<br>
<br>
- Serraghost <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p075.ezboard.com/bascension10244.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zariarz>ZariaRZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#333333>(6/21/04 12:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p075.ezboard.com/fascension10244frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2728.topic&index=64>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Hell enchanters dont need anymore offense...they still have ways to get points. Honestly if you look at the points thing some of the people with the most points dont have shit for kills. Its from them being grouped and assisting in them but they dont necessarly have to be the one getting the ks.<br>
